EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO STATE AFFAIRS AND GOVERNMENT -- CORRECTIONS DEPARTMENT
***
1 This act would set standards and procedures to allow and implement conjugal visitation at
2 state correctional facilities. This act also directs the department of corrections to establish and
3 enforce rules and regulations governing conjugal visits.
4 This act would take effect on January 1, 2026.
